0period%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHynes%20and%20Amormino%20planned%20their%20mini-retirement%20to%20last%20roughly%20six%20months%2C%20during%20which%20they%20visited%20seven%20different%20countries%3A%20Tanzania%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20Georgia%2C%20and%20Italy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20went%20on%20a%20safari%2C%20took%20cooking%20courses%2C%20hiked%2C%20and%20got%20to%20know%20locals%20through%20homestays%20and%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20goal%20was%20to%20step%20away%20from%20the%20sometimes%20monotonous%20routine%20of%20our%20day%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Hynes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erin%20Hynes%20and%20Lucus%20Amormino%20on%20safari%20in%20Tanzania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4ea671aa2ac29ee32a382%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHynes%20and%20Amormino%20ticked%20off%20Tanzania%20from%20their%20travel%20bucket%20list.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erin%20Hynes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20Hynes%20embarked%20on%20a%20similar%20trip%2C%20she%20was%2026.%20She%20had%20finished%20graduate%20school%20and%20decided%20to%20fly%20to%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20where%20Amormino%20was%20based%20for%20part%20of%20his%20MBA%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20program%20ended%2C%20the%20couple%20spent%20months%20traveling%20through%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20ended%20somewhat%20abruptly%20when%20Hynes%20ran%20out%20of%20money.%20She%20owed%20%241%2C000%20on%20her%20credit%20card%20and%20felt%20obligated%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20return%20to%20Canada%20and%20call%20up%20her%20dad%20for%20a%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20first%20paycheck%20that%20I%20got%2C%20once%20I%20was%20employed%2C%20I%20immediately%20sent%20him%20%24500%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20them%20to%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20irresponsibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20didn't%20deter%20Hynes%20or%20her%20husband%20from%20planning%20another%20big%20trip.%20She%20said%20they%20spoke%20for%20years%20about%20doing%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20repeat%20offender%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226cd33034-bc0e-48ec-b2b1-de2c7a7839e0%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20spent%20over%205%20years%20planning%20for%20their%20career%20break%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHynes%20said%20she%20and%20Amormino%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20avoid%20falling%20into%20financial%20insecurity%20this%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20five%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20we%20had%20actively%20been%20discussing%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20do%20a%20trip%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20sort%20of%20left%20it%20at%2C%20'Let's%20just%20aggressively%20save%2C%20and%20when%20the%20right%20moment%20comes%2C%20we%20will%20know%20that%20it%20is%20time.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20that%20time%20came%2C%20they%20had%2040%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%2C%20around%20%2429%2C360%2C%20saved%20up%20purely%20for%20travel%2C%20as%20well%20as%2020%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%2C%20around%20%2414%2C680%2C%20as%20a%20buffer%20in%20case%20they%20found%20it%20tricky%20to%20find%20new%20jobs%20when%20they%20came%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHynes%20said%20she%20also%20began%20to%20earn%20money%20from%20her%20blog%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpinatravels.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPina%20Travels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20through%20advertising%20and%20affiliate%20marketing%20and%20brand%20partnerships.%20They%20put%20the%20additional%20income%20toward%20their%20buffer%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20important%20to%20us%20that%20we%20had%20a%20specific%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20spend%20that%20didn't%20touch%20our%20retirement%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Erin%20Hynes%20and%20Lucus%20Amormino%20during%20a%20cooking%20course%20in%20Nepal.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4eb015da406397bf751ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHynes%20and%20Amormino%20immersed%20themselves%20in%20local%20cultures%20by%20taking%20cooking%20courses%20and%20booking%20homestays.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Erin%20Hynes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20kept%20costs%20down%20on%20the%20trip%20by%20doing%20homestays%20and%20booking%20guest%20houses%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20accommodation%20as%20well%20as%20having%20a%20flexible%20itinerary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTraveling%20that%20way%20%E2%80%94%20without%20too%20much%20of%20a%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20it%20cheaper%20because%20we%20could%20tap%20into%20the%20flight%20deals%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20meticulous%20planning%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20of%20their%20family%20and%20friends%20were%20supportive%2C%20they%20felt%20some%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20around%20us%2C%20they're%20at%20the%20stage%20where%20they're%20having%20kids%2C%20they're%20buying%20houses.%20And%20we're%20doing%20not%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20are%20almost%20100%25%20confident%20they%20won't%20have%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ccb82fe-046f-4494-a132-337cd620cc72%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20couple%20relied%20on%20their%20networks%20to%20get%20jobs%20after%20traveling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20May%20rolled%20around%2C%20after%20about%20five%20months%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20to%20feel%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20the%20money%20running%20out%2C%20and%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20now%20we%20have%20to%20adult%20again%20and%20think%20about%20our%20return%20home%2C'%26