0argue%20that%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20these%20topics%20may%20perpetuate%20harmful%20attitudes%20towards%20marginalized%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20time%20to%20have%20a%20relook%20at%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20various%20components%20in%20the%20existing%20regulations%20and%20guidelines%2C%20and%20adapt%20them%20to%20the%20changing%20demography%2C%20socio-economic%20context%2C%20perceptions%2C%20values%2C%20advancements%20in%20medical%20education%20and%20expectations%20of%20stakeholders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NMC%20said%20in%20its%20Competency-Based%20Medical%20Education%20Curriculum%20(CBME)%20Guidelines%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revised%20curriculum%20also%20focuses%20on%20medico-legal%20frameworks%2C%20codes%20of%20conduct%2C%20and%20medical%20ethics%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20alignment%20and%20integration%20of%20subjects.%20The%20commission%20said%20it%20aims%20to%20produce%20a%20primary%20care%20physician%20with%20skills%20in%20promotive%2C%20preventative%2C%20rehabilitative%2C%20palliative%20care%2C%20and%20referral%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20contact%20physician%20needs%20to%20be%20skilful%20to%20perform%20duties%20of%20primary%20care%20physician%20and%20have%20requisite%20skills%20for%20promotive%2C%20preventative%2C%20rehabilitative%2C%20palliative%20care%20and%20referral%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20raised%20concerns%20among%20medical%20professionals%20and%20LGBTQ%2B%20advocates%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20the%20changes%20may%20undermine%20progress%20made%20in%20promoting%20inclusivity%20and%20understanding%20in%20medical%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725442260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fcqbl6u5g_medical-student-generic_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsodomy-lesbianism-are-unnatural-sex-offences-new-textbook-for