t%20riding%20in%20a%20robot%20taxi%20is%20that%20it%20feels%20very%2C%20very%20weird.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20thing%20to%20know%20is%20that%2C%20weirdly%2C%20riding%20in%20a%20robot%20taxi%20quickly%20starts%20to%20feel%20completely%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20a%20car%20that%20drives%20itself%20is%20as%20old%20as%20science%20fiction.%20But%20the%20push%20for%20autonomous%20auto%20tech%20didn't%20get%20underway%20in%20earnest%20until%20about%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-first-self-driving-cars-that-competed-in-darpa-grand-challenge-2015-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDARPA%20started%20running%20contests%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20who%20could%20actually%20build%20a%20driverless%20vehicle.%20Two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Google%20spinoff%20Waymo%20and%20the%20GM%20subsidiary%20Cruise%20finally%20deployed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F8-ways-driverless-cars-will-drastically-improve-our-lives-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecars%20without%20drivers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20go%20great.%20Just%20one%20day%20after%20Cruise%20started%20running%20its%20Uber-like%20ride-hailing%20service%2C%20a%20dozen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-san-francisco-robocabs-stalled-outside-lands-traffic-cars-california-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eof%20its%20cars%20coalesced%20into%20a%20swarm%20traffic%20jam%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Last%20year%2C%20after%20getting%20hit%20by%20a%20human-driven%20car%2C%20a%20pedestrian%20fell%20to%20the%20street%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Cruise%20robot%2C%20which%20ran%20them%20over.%20Detecting%20a%20collision%2C%20the%20robot%20drove%2020%20feet%20forward%20and%20stopped%20at%20the%20curbside%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-cruise-self-driving-robotaxis-were-banned-in-san-francisco-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edragging%20the%20person%20underneath%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruise%20got%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcruise-self-driving-robotaxis-all-time-low-mo-elshenawy-staff-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebanned%20from%20the%20city%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20today%2C%20Waymo's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-self-driving-taxis-chipotle-robots-future-of-service-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etricked-out%20Jaguar%20SUVs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20fender-mounted%20lidar%20sensors%20spinning%20like%20medieval%20banners%20heralding%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20king%20%E2%80%94%20are%20ubiquitous%20in%20San%20Francisco.%20Kids%20wave%20at%20them%3B%20tourists%20take%20pictures.%20At%20first%2C%20access%20was%20limited%2C%20by%20invitation%20only.%20But%20in%20July%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-test-drive-san-francisco-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20service%20opened%20to%20anyone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20willing%20to%20download%20an%20app%20and%20type%20in%20a%20credit-card%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20writing%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Freport-la-coming-home-159137%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecities%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fputting-charge-back-driving-178218%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etransportation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20so%20I%20know%20that%20it's%20exceedingly%20rare%20for%20a%20new%20mode%20of%20transport%20to%20appear.%20Planes%2C%20trains%2C%20and%20automobiles%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20pretty%20much%20the%20history%20of%20the%20past%20two%20centuries%20of%20people%20getting%20from%20here%20to%20there%20in%20new%20ways.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20spend%20a%20few%20weeks%20riding%20around%20in%20Waymo's%20cars%2C%20to%20see%20what%20our%20robot-driven%20future%20looks%20like.%20I%20used%20them%20for%20running%20errands%2C%20the%20same%20as%20I%20might%20rely%20on%20Uber%20or%20Lyft.%20I%20also%20spent%20a%20day%20gallivanting%20around%20town%20in%20a%20more%20touristy%20way%2C%20to%20see%20what%20longer%20and%20more%20challenging%20routes%20felt%20like.%20I've%20come%20away%20convinced%20that%20self-driving%20cars%20are%20going%20to%20alter%20some%20fundamental%20things%20about%20America's%20cities%2C%20and%20how%20we%20get%20around%20them%20%E2%80%94%20for%20better%20and%20for%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20hailed%20my%20first%20Waymo%2C%20I%20expected%20that%20riding%20in%20a%20robot%20cab%20was%20going%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20cozy%20version%20of%20the%20future.%20A%20car%20that%20drives%20itself%3F%20As%20a%20kid%2C%20I%20always%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20waited%20long%20enough%2C%20%26quot%3BKnight%20Rider%26quot%3B%20would%20come%20true.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETurbo-boosted%20Super%20Pursuit%20Mode%2C%20here%20I%20come!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20call%20a%20Waymo%2C%20the%20waiting%20part%20of%20the%20experience%20is%20certainly%20familiar.%20You%20request%20a%20ride%2C%20and%20the%20app%20tells%20you%20how%20far%20away%20the%20car%20is%20and%20when%20to%20expect%20it.%20When%20the%20robot%20pulls%20up%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20beacon%20on%20top%20illuminates%20with%20your%20initials.%20You%20unlock%20the%20car%20by%20touching%20the%20app%2C%20and%20the%20handles%20unfold%20from%20flush%20against%20the%20door%2C%20like%20guns%20on%20a%20Transformer.%20Waymo's%20head%20of%20UX%20design%2C%20Lauren%20Schwendimann%2C%20tells%20me%20the%20doors%20are%20activated%20by%20the%20phone%20talking%20directly%20to%20the%20car%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first%20bit%20of%20hand-holding%20in%20the%20new%20relationship%20between%20human%20and%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGet%20in%2C%20and%20the%20car%20greets%20you%20by%20name.%20Very%20chill%20ambient%20music%20plays%2C%20to%20get%20you%20in%20a%20Westworld%20frame%20of%20mind.%20Tap%20the%20touchscreen%20facing%20the%20back%20seat%20to%20tell%20the%20car%20you're%20ready%2C%20and%20off%20you%20go%2C%20with%20the%20screen%20providing%20a%20video-game-like%20view%20of%20the%20car's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20riders%20feel%20like%20everything%20is%20going%20to%20be%20OK.%20%26quot%3BWe%20very%20much%20curate%20that%20to%20achieve%20this%20relaxed%20feel%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwendimann%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20ride%20other%20forms%20of%20transportation%2C%20you're%20in%20other%20people's%20space.%20There's%20value%20to%20public%20transportation%2C%20but%20there%20is%20something%20about%20having%20space%20to%20yourself%20and%20that%20moment%20of%20quiet%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20peace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20sure%2C%20it's%20calming%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20point.%20For%20me%20that%20point%20was%20when%20the%20car%20pulled%20away%20from%20the%20curb%20and%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20empty%20driver's%20seat.%20The%20steering%20wheel%20was%20turning%20of%20its%20own%20volition%2C%20as%20if%20I%20were%20being%20driven%20by%20a%20ghost.%20What%20I%20thought%20was%2C%20%3Cem%3Eholy%20shit!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20riding%20in%20my%20first%20Waymo%2C%20I%20hadn't%20considered%20that%20when%20people%20called%20the%20first%20automobile%20a%20%26quot%3Bhorseless%20carriage%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20must%20have%20been%20out%20of%20abject%20horror.%20The%20thing%20moved%20like%20a%20carriage%20%E2%80%A6%20but%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethere's%20no%20horse!%20%3Cem%3EThere's%20no%20horse!%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESpooky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20everyone%20who%20takes%20a%20Waymo%20experiences%20the%20same%20ghost-panic.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20we%20know%20that%20is%20a%20very%20prominent%20feature%20of%20the%20ride%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwendimann%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20contributes%20to%20the%20sense%20of%20wonder%20and%20awe.%26quot%3B%20That's%20mainly%20because%20robot%20cars%2C%20like%20every%20other%20vehicle%20on%20a%20city%20street%2C%20are%20required%20to%20have%20a%20functional%20steering%20wheel.%20In%20a%20Waymo%2C%20the%20driver's-side%20door%20doesn't%20even%20unlock.%20But%20once%20Waymo%20and%20other%20companies%20are%20permitted%20to%20roll%20out%20more%20Westworldly%2C%20podlike%20vehicles%2C%20without%20any%20driver%20controls%2C%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20turn%20the%20space%20normally%20inhabited%20by%20a%20driver%20over%20to%20passengers.%20There%20won't%20be%20any%20%26quot%3Bfront%20seat.%26quot%3B%20Younger%20siblings%20will%20weep%2C%20for%20there%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bshotgun!%26quot%3B%20to%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20worth%20pausing%20to%20appreciate%20that%20hardly%20anyone%20on%20Earth%20has%20ever%20been%20alone%20in%20a%20moving%20automobile%20without%20being%20the%20driver.%20This%20is%20an%20entirely%20new%20sensation%2C%20and%20let%20me%20tell%20you%2C%20it's%20destabilizing.%20As%20the%20steering%20wheel%20rotates%2C%20the%20car's%20screens%20display%20your%20progress%20through%20the%20city's%20streets%2C%20re-rendered%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20phantom%20zone.%20Buildings%20appear%20as%20barely%20there%20outlines.%20Other%20cars%20are%20bluish%20apparitions%2C%20while%20pedestrians%20and%20cyclists%20glow%20a%20vibrant%2C%20flickering%20orange-red.%20The%20closest%20sensation%20I%20could%20think%20of%20is%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthemedenvironments.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F03%2Ftheme-park-101-layout-is-everything.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edark%20ride%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20at%20an%20amusement%20park%2C%20where%20everyone%20piles%20into%20an%20automated%20boat%20or%20a%20spaceship%20and%20gets%20pushed%20through%20an%20illuminated%20story%20populated%20by%20animatronic%20characters.%20You%20know%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fpassport2dreams.blogspot.com%2F2011%2F08%2Ffire-in-night-pre-eminent-attraction-as.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPirates%20of%20the%20Caribbean%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20It's%20a%20Small%20World%3F%20Waymo%20is%20Mr.%20Toad's%20Mild%20Ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20display%20is%20intended%20to%20help%20keep%20the%20rider%20grounded%2C%20as%20it%20were.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20show%20in%20the%20scene%20are%20things%20to%20help%20the%20rider%20orient%20to%20where%20they%20are%20and%20understand%20the%20basics%20of%20where%20the%20car%20is%20going%20to%20go%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwendimann%20says.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20the%20eerie%20screen%20view%20only%20added%20to%20the%20surreality.%20London%20cabbies%20used%20to%20get%20licensed%20based%20on%20their%20command%20of%20the%20Knowledge%2C%20a%20truly%20encyclopedic%20sense%20of%20how%20to%20get%20around%20London's%20thousand-year-old%20streets%3B%20neuroscientists%20found%20that%20drivers%20who%20acquired%20this%20mastery%20of%20spatial%20memory%20literally%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1016%2Fj.cub.2011.11.018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebigger%20brains%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Yet%20here%20I%20was%2C%20sitting%20inside%20a%20robot%20programmed%20with%20San%20Francisco%20Knowledge%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20my%20brain%20was%20getting%20smaller%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20outsourcing.%20The%20screen%20displayed%20no%20street%20names%3B%20the%20buildings%20were%20unidentifiable%20apparitions.%20I%20couldn't%20even%20ask%20the%20driver%20to%20take%20a%20more%20scenic%20route%2C%20or%20to%20pull%20over%20while%20I%20grabbed%20some%20coffee.%20I%20felt%20oddly%20alienated%20from%20the%20city%20I%20was%20moving%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20consumer%20perspective%2C%20my%20Waymo%20experience%20was%20about%20on%20par%20with%20taking%20an%20Uber.%20Waymo%20was%20generally%20cheaper%2C%20and%20equally%20reliable.%20It%20sometimes%20took%20what%20seemed%20like%20slower%2C%20back-street%20routes.%20And%20it%20once%20canceled%20my%20pickup%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20North%20Beach%20just%20after%20a%20police%20car%20had%20rolled%20up%20nearby%2C%20sirens%20blaring%20and%20lights%20flashing%2C%20and%20brought%20traffic%20around%20me%20to%20a%20stop.%20But%2C%20flip%20side%2C%20the%20other%20day%20my%20Lyft%20driver%2C%20who%20seemed%20to%20have%20trouble%20following%20the%20directions%20on%20his%20phone%2C%20got%20lost.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESo%20%E2%80%A6%20robot%20gets%20five%20stars%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20weirdest%20part%20of%20taking%20a%20Waymo%20is%20how%20quickly%20it%20stops%20feeling%20weird.%20Once%20you've%20heard%20the%20onboarding%20spiel%20a%20couple%20of%20times%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20starts%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20bit%20like%2C%20well%2C%20riding%20in%20a%20cab.%20And%20after%20the%20novelty%20of%20the%20empty%20driver's%20seat%20wears%20off%2C%20the%20temptation%20to%20just%20pull%20out%20your%20phone%20and%20doomscroll%20your%20way%20to%20the%20next%20destination%20is%20powerful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20to%20say%2C%20it's%20shocking%20to%20be%20reminded%20of%20how%20quickly%20we%20begin%20to%20take%20the%20marvels%20of%20our%20world%20for%20granted.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20during%20my%20second%20ride%2C%20I%20reset%20the%20music%20from%20its%20futuristic%20ambient%20default%20setting%20to%20Classic%20EDM.%20But%20the%20next%20time%20I%20got%20into%20a%20Waymo%2C%20the%20futuristic%20ambient%20default%20was%20playing%20again.%20And%20I%20got%20%3Cem%3Emad%3C%2Fem%3E!%20This%20self-driving%2C%20autonomous%20robot%20from%20the%20future%20can't%20even%20be%20bothered%20to%20remember%20my%20preference%20for%20Aphex%20Twin%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tell%20Schwendimann%20about%20this%2C%20she%20laughs%20at%20me%2C%20which%20I%20deserve.%20Then%20she%20assures%20me%20that%20they're%20working%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20customization%20settings%20%E2%80%94%20music%2C%20interior%20lighting%2C%20whatever.%20Whichever%20car%20picks%20you%20up%20should%20feel%20like%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20car%2C%20she%20says.%20That's%20part%20of%20feeling%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202015%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2016%2F01%2Fthe-metastructure-transportation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EI%20rode%20in%20one%20of%20Google's%20experimental%20versions%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20self-driving%20car%2C%20with%20a%20human%20backup%20sitting%20behind%20the%20wheel.%20The%20car%20drove%20like%20a%2016-year-old%20who%20just%20got%20their%20learner's%20permit.%20Every%20stop%20sign%2C%20every%20pedestrian%20on%20a%20sidewalk%2C%20even%20the%20occasional%20tree%20would%20cause%20the%20robot%20to%20slam%20on%20the%20brakes%20hard%20enough%20to%20bounce%20my%20head%20off%20the%20headrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo's%20Jags%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20drive%20like%20a%20competent%20and%20cautious%20professional.%20Riding%20in%20them%20gets%20a%20little%20boring%20in%20part%20because%20they%20are%20uncannily%20good.%20We%20slipped%20deftly%20past%20a%20double-parked%20food-delivery%20driver%20%E2%80%94%20signaled%2C%20juked%20left%2C%20signaled%2C%20juked%20back%20right%20%E2%80%94%20amid%20Chinatown%20traffic.%20We%20changed%20lanes%20with%20confidence%2C%20maintained%20steady%20speeds%20on%20San%20Francisco's%20challenging%20hills.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20a%20driver%20with%20no%20patience%20for%20the%20Waymo's%20steady%2C%20speed-limit-abiding%20pace%20raced%20up%20behind%20us%20and%20pulled%20into%20a%20red-painted%20buses-only%20lane%20on%20our%20left%20to%20pass.%20The%20illegal%20move%20seemed%20to%20freak%20the%20Waymo%20out%20for%20a%20second%20%E2%80%94%20it%20paused%2C%20slowed%20way%20down.%20But%20then%20we%20got%20going%20again.%20(And%20yes%2C%20I%20realize%20it's%20weird%20to%20refer%20to%20myself%20and%20a%20robot%20car%20as%20%26quot%3Bwe.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20own%20life%20I%20drive%20a%20faster-than-you'd-expect%20little%20hatchback%2C%20and%20I'll%20admit%20that%20I%20sometimes%20drive%20faster%20than%20you'd%20expect.%20But%20in%20some%20circumstances%20the%20Waymos%20were%20actually%20more%20aggressive%20than%20I%20would've%20been.%20Last%20week%20I%20induced%20my%20kids%20to%20come%20robot-riding%20with%20me%2C%20bribed%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20blowout%20back-to-school%20lunch%20at%20Swan%20Oyster%20Depot.%20We%20went%20ranging%20around%20town%2C%20including%20a%20long%20drive%20that%20put%20us%20on%20Portola%20Drive%2C%20a%20curving%20and%20hilly%20extension%20of%20the%20city's%20spinal%20main%20drag.%20The%20Waymo%20took%20those%20curves%20faster%20and%20more%20affirmatively%20than%20I%20would%20have.%20At%20least%20one%20driver%20even%20honked%20at%20us%20as%20we%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20%26quot%3Bcut%20him%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20a%20robot%20would%20never.%20But%20the%20other%20guy%20leaned%20on%20his%20horn%2C%20which%2C%20when%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20is%20kind%20of%20hilarious.%20The%20war%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-cybertruck-apocalypse-inequality-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eroad%3C%2Fu%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cu%3E%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cu%3Emachines%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20begins%20with%20road%20rage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ERobots%20are%20clearly%20fantastic%20at%20doing%20car-like%20things.%20The%20question%20is%2C%20do%20we%20%3Cem%3Ewant%3C%2Fem%3E%20more%20technology%20that%20does%20car-like%20things%3F%20Cars%20are%20flexible%2C%20fast%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20can%20go%20pretty%20much%20anywhere%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there's%20pavement%20and%20parking.%20So%20American%20cities%20basically%20gave%20them%20priority%20after%20World%20War%20II%2C%20ripping%20up%20trolley%20tracks%20and%20ramming%20new%20freeways%20through%20low-income%20and%20minority%20neighborhoods%20in%20the%20service%20of%20speed%2C%20suburban%20convenience%2C%20and%20petrochemical%20profits.%20But%20technological%20choices%20have%20consequences.%20The%20rise%20of%20cars%20fueled%20traffic%20jams%2C%20air%20pollution%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20income%20inequality%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froad-rage-speeding-driving-traffic-large-expensive-cars-suv-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edeath%20and%20misery%20from%20car%20crashes%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%20about%2020%25%20of%20America's%20downtowns%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fparkingreform.org%2Fresources%2Fparking-lot-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edevoted%20to%20parking%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20as%20many%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Farticle%2F10.1088%2F1748-9326%2F5%2F3%2F034001%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E2%20billion%20spaces%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobot%20cars%20don't%20do%20much%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20to%20alleviate%20these%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20may%20make%20them%20worse.%20The%20biggest%20problem%20that%20robot%20cars%20%26quot%3Bsolve%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20cost%20of%20human%20labor.%20Instead%20of%20paying%20a%20living%20wage%20to%20cabbies%2C%20tech%20companies%20have%20spent%20billions%20of%20dollars%20developing%20robots%20to%20take%20their%20place.%20(Both%20Lyft%20and%20Uber%20have%20indicated%20that%20they%20envision%20their%20future%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyd-uber-partnership-electric-vehicles-discount-autonomous-self-driving-tesla-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efull%20of%20robot%20drivers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20The%20money%20goes%20up%20the%20line%2C%20to%20programmers%2C%20managers%2C%20and%20investors.%20Science%20has%20essentially%20discovered%20a%20way%20to%20increase%20profits%20by%20combining%20the%20social%20isolation%20and%20environmental%20degradation%20of%20the%20automobile%20with%20the%20frustration%20and%20ennui%20of%20public%20transit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20really%2C%20the%20experience%20of%20sitting%20alone%20in%20a%20robot%20car%20is%20more%20than%20that.%20Will%20people%20use%20the%20opportunity%20to%20turn%20off%20the%20surveillance%20cameras%20and%20have%20sex%3F%20Probably%3A%20They%20used%20to%20do%20that%20on%20the%20gondola%20ride%20at%20Disneyland%2C%20too.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20women%2C%20racial%20minorities%2C%20and%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%20encounter%20all%20sorts%20of%20harassment%20and%20outright%20violence%20as%20they%20move%20through%20cities.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-sexual-assault-43-percent-by-passengers-report-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERide%20hailing%20is%20particularly%20bad%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20that%3A%20Drivers%20harass%20lone%20passengers%2C%20and%20passengers%20harass%20drivers.%20Most%20of%20the%20conversation%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20robot%20cars%20has%20been%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmissy-cummings-robot-taxis-tesla-elon-musk-autonomous-cruise-waymo-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewhat%20happens%20when%20they%20hit%20someone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20they%20inevitably%20will.%20But%20the%20space%20%3Cem%3Einside%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20robot%20taxi%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20safe%20for%20people%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%20because%20there's%20no%20one%20there%20to%20mess%20with%20you.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20few%20ways%20to%20get%20around%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20urban%20landscape%20where%20you%20can%20be%20truly%20alone.%20If%20one%20metric%20for%20evaluating%20a%20city%20is%20how%20safely%20people%20and%20things%20can%20move%20through%20it%2C%20robot%20cabs%20will%20make%20cities%20measurably%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20autonomous%20vehicles%20are%20a%20literal%20transport%20of%20delight%2C%20a%20miraculous%20and%20liberating%20technology.%20And%20on%20the%20other%2C%20they%20magnify%20all%20the%20scary%20economics%2C%20bad%20ethics%2C%20weird%20sociology%2C%20and%20redistribution%20of%20wealth%20that%20cars%20helped%20usher%20in%20almost%20exactly%20a%20century%20ago.%20Pluses%20and%20minuses!%20Philosophers%20call%20that%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.5840%2Ftechne2019722100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etechnological%20sublime%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20it's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20imagine%20American%20cities%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-build-infrastructure-transportation-housing-regulation-environment-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebuilding%20any%20grand%20new%20infrastructure%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20no%20protected%20bike%20lanes%2C%20no%20new%20trolleys%20or%20subway%20lines%20or%20high-speed%20rail%20%E2%80%94%20robot%20taxis%20are%20what%20we%20get.%20Robots%2C%20after%20all%2C%20don't%20jeopardize%20the%20twin%20North%20Stars%20of%20what%20passes%20for%20urban%20planning%20in%20America%3A%20free%20parking%20and%20the%20freedom%20to%20drive%20fast.%20Maybe%20that's%20why%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20in%20the%20world%20is%20being%20allowed%20to%20field%20test%202-ton%20experimental%20robots%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20a%20major%20American%20city.%20Robot%20cars%20will%20never%20take%20up%20a%20parking%20space.%20They%20will%20never%20require%20us%2C%20horror%20of%20horrors%2C%20to%20take%20a%20bus%20or%20a%20train.%20Instead%20they%20will%20blend%20invisibly%20into%20the%20world%20we've%20already%20built.%20Just%20a%20ghost%20in%20a%20dysfunctional%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emachine%2C%20taking%20us%20for%20a%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fadam-rogers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdam%20Rogers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robot-taxis-weird-san-francisco-traffic-parking-cars-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725441842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c62eb01aa2ac29ee330a09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robot-taxis-weird-san-francisco-traffic-parking-cars-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Riding%20around%20in%20a%20robot%20cab%20feels%20totally%20futuristic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20strangely%20normal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arogers%40businessinsider.com%20(Adam%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robot-taxis-weird-san-francisco-traffic-parking-cars-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Relief%20Yet%20For%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%2C%20She%20Claims%20Court%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20movie%20'Emergency'%2C%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20row%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20opposed%20its%20release%2C%20got%20no%20relief%20from%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20today.%20The%20court%20said%20it%20cannot%20ask%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20to%20issue%20a%20certificate%20to%20the%20film's%20makers%20as%20it%20would%20contradict%20a%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setback%2C%20the%20actor%20and%20BJP%20MP%20claimed%20a%20win%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BHigh%20court%20has%20blasted%20censor%20for%20illegally%20withholding%20the%20certificate%20of%20%23emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20is%20co-produced%20by%20Ms%20Ranaut's%20Manikarnika%20Films%20and%20Zee%20Studios.%20With%20the%20film%20earlier%20scheduled%20for%20a%20release%20on%20September%206%2C%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20Censor%20Board%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20that%20would%20clear%20the%20decks%20for%20the%20film's%20release.%20The%20setback%20in%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20means%20that%20the%20movie%20is%20unlikely%20to%20release%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-emergency-release-date-sensitive-content-government-sources-6473532%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSensitive%20Content%26quot%3B%3A%20Government%20Sources%20On%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20'%3Ci%3EEmergency%3C%2Fi%3E'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%2C%20based%20on%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201975%2C%20ran%20into%20trouble%20after%20the%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%2C%20the%20apex%20religious%20body%20for%20Sikhs%2C%20alleged%20that%20it%20misrepresents%20Sikhs%20and%20sought%20a%20ban.%20Ms%20Ranaut%20later%20said%20the%20Censor%20Board%20had%20put%20on%20hold%20the%20certificate%20issued%20to%20her%20film.%20Sources%20in%20the%20government%20said%20some%20religious%20organisations%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20film.%20%26quot%3BReligious%20sentiments%20cannot%20be%20hurt.%20There%20is%20some%20sensitive%20content%20in%20the%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Centre%20was%20seriously%20looking%20at%20the%20concerns.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-stuck-in-massive-row-what-are-the-objections-6487046%5C%22%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20'Emergency'%20Stuck%20In%20Massive%20Row.%20What%20Are%20The%20Objections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20Sikh%20organisations%20filed%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20against%20the%20movie%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court.%20In%20its%20response%2C%20the%20Censor%20Board%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20movie%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20a%20certificate.%20The%20court%20then%20disposed%20of%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20the%20matter%20in%20court%2C%20Zee's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Venkatesh%20Dhond%2C%20told%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BP%20Colabawalla%20and%20Justice%20Firdosh%20Pooniwalla%20that%20CBFC%20informed%20Manikarnika%20Films%20on%20August%208%20that%20film%20is%20suitable%20for%20unrestricted%20public%20exhibition%2C%20subject%20to%20some%20modifications.%20On%20August%2014%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20film's%20makers%20submitted%20the%20film%20to%20CBFC%20with%20the%20modifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20Manikarnika%20received%20an%20email%20from%20CBFC%20stating%20that%20the%20CD%20is%20sealed%20and%20requested%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20to%20collect%20the%20certificate.%20But%20later%2C%20the%20certificate%20was%20not%20handed%20over%2C%20apparently%20following%20the%20opposition%20from%20Sikh%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhond%20agued%20that%20CBFC%20is%20a%20censor%20body%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20an%20authority%20to%20look%20after%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20maker%20of%20the%20film%20is%20a%20sitting%20MP.%20They%20gave%20her%20a%20censor%20certificate%20and%20could%20have%20simply%20said%2C%20look%20we%20have%20given%20the%20censor%20certificate%20and%20now%20if%20there%20is%20unrest%2C%20the%20State%20can%20take%20care%20of%20the%20same.%20They%20cannot%20say%20that%20now%20that%20there%20is%20an%20unrest%2C%20we%20will%20rethink%20the%20certification.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20CBFC%2C%20Advocate%20Abhinav%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20certificate%20is%20not%20issued%20until%20it%20is%20signed%20by%20the%20Censor%20Board's%20chairperson.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20cannot%20ask%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20as%20it%20would%20be%20in%20breach%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20rejected%20CBFC's%20contention%20that%20the%20certificate%20had%20not%20been%20issued%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20the%20makers%20comply%20with%20the%20modifications%20required%20by%20the%20CBFC%20and%20the%20CD%20with%20modifications%20is%20sealed%20successfully%2C%20we%20have%20to%20presume%20that%20the%20CBFC%20applied%20its%20mind%20and%20thereafter%20issued%20the%20email%20to%20Manikarnika%20that%20the%20CD%20of%20the%20film%20is%20successfully%20sealed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court's%20order%20was%20based%20on%20the%20Centre's%20submission%20that%20the%20film%20isn't%20certified%20yet%20and%20that%20it%20is%20under%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20relief%20to%20the%20film's%20makers%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20unable%20to%20pass%20this%20direction%20in%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20MP%20High%20Court%20has%20specifically%20directed%20the%20CBFC%20to%20consider%20the%20representations%20of%20the%20Jabalpur%20Sikh%20Sangat%20before%20certifying%20the%20film.%20If%20we%20were%20to%20direct%20the%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%2C%20we%20would%20have%20breached%20the%20division%20bench's%20directive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudicial%20Propriety%20demands%20such%20orders%20ought%20not%20be%20passed.%20We%20therefore%2C%20are%20unable%20to%20direct%20the%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20certificate%20as%20sought%20by%20the%20petitioner.%20We%20however%2C%20do%20not%20dispose%20of%20the%20present%20petition.%20And%20we%20direct%20the%20C