illegal%20WiFi%20network%20on%20a%20warship%2C%20a%20new%20report%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrisel%20Marrero%20installed%20a%20Starlink%20network%20on%20the%20USS%20Manchester%20and%20named%20it%20%26quot%3BSTINKY.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20lied%20to%20and%20misled%20her%20commanding%20officer%20at%20least%20three%20times%20when%20questioned%20about%20the%20network%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20US%20Navy%20enlisted%20leader%20who%20was%20demoted%20after%20she%20was%20caught%20running%20illegal%20WiFi%20on%20a%20warship%20used%20a%20leadership%20association's%20debit%20card%20to%20pay%20for%20its%20monthly%20bills%20and%20named%20it%20%26quot%3BSTINKY%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrisel%20Marrero%2C%20who%20was%20the%20command%20senior%20chief%20of%20the%20USS%20Manchester%2C%20installed%20and%20operated%20the%20unauthorized%20network%20during%20a%20deployment%20in%202023%2C%20lying%20to%20her%20commanders%20and%20falsifying%20records%20to%20cover%20up%20its%20presence%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Navy%20charge%20sheet%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20judgment%20filed%20on%20May%2029%2C%20%3Cspan%3EMarrero%20was%20demoted%20from%20senior%20chief%20petty%20officer%20to%20chief%20petty%20officer%20%3C%2Fspan%3Eafter%20being%20found%20guilty%20of%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20and%20providing%20false%20official%20statements%20to%20her%20commanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-navy%2F2024%2F09%2F03%2Fhow-navy-chiefs-conspired-to-get-themselves-illegal-warship-wi-fi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENavy%20Times%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20documents%20from%20a%20Navy%20investigation%2C%20reveals%20new%20information%20on%20Marrero's%20conduct%2C%20saying%20she%20worked%20secretly%20with%20other%20enlisted%20chiefs%20to%20install%20and%20maintain%20a%20%241%2C000-a-month%20Starlink%20network%20on%20the%20Manchester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarrero%20had%20paid%20for%20the%20%242%2C800%20Starlink%20dish%20and%20kit%20with%20a%20personal%20credit%20card%20and%20was%20the%20network%20administrator%2C%20maintaining%20the%20sole%20authority%20to%20add%20others%20to%20the%20network%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20another%20chief%20installed%20the%20dish%20on%20the%20Manchester's%20weather%20deck%20during%20a%20blanket%20%26quot%3Baloft%26quot%3B%20period%20when%20duties%20aren't%20recorded%20in%20the%20ship's%20logs%2C%20per%20Navy%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Marrero%20had%20paid%20for%20the%20dish%20with%20a%20personal%20credit%20card%2C%20the%20chiefs%20on%20the%20Manchester%20split%20the%20cost%20of%20Starlink's%20recurring%20bills%20and%20paid%20them%20with%20a%20Chief%20Petty%20Officer%20Association%20debit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief's%20mess%20then%20kept%20access%20to%20the%20Starlink%20network%20%E2%80%94%20which%20they%20named%20%26quot%3BSTINKY%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20themselves%2C%20Navy%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20junior%20sailors%20and%20commanding%20officers%20began%20noticing%20the%20WiFi%20network%2C%20Marrero%20denied%20its%20existence%2C%20according%20to%20Navy%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarrero's%20charge%20sheet%20said%20she%20lied%20to%20her%20commanding%20officer%20on%20at%20least%20three%20occasions%20from%20July%20to%20August%202023%2C%20telling%20them%20each%20time%20that%20there%20was%20no%20WiFi%20onboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20she%20changed%20the%20network's%20name%20from%20%26quot%3BSTINKY%26quot%3B%20to%20something%20that%20sounded%20like%20a%20wireless%20printer%2C%20although%20there%20were%20no%20such%20printers%20on%20the%20ship%2C%20Navy%20Times%20wrote%2C%20citing%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Starlink%20dish%20was%20eventually%20discovered%20on%20August%2018%20by%20a%20civilian%20installing%20a%20separate%2C%20authorized%20satellite%20communication%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20gig%20is%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Marrero%20texted%20a%20crew%20member%20at%20the%20time%2C%20according%20to%20the%20investigation%20seen%20by%20Navy%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20confronted%2C%20she%20and%20the%20other%20chiefs%20tried%20to%20remove%20the%20dish%2C%20then%20told%20commanders%20that%20they%20only%20used%20it%20while%20in%20port%2C%20per%20Navy%20Times.%20Marrero's%20charge%20sheet%20also%20said%20that%20she%20altered%20data%20usage%20records%20for%20the%20Starlink%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENavy%20Times%20reported%20that%20Marrero%20admitted%20to%20her%20commanding%20officer%20on%20August%2026%2C%202023%2C%20that%20she%20had%20installed%20the%20illegal%20WiFi%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20records%20show%20that%20Marrero%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20two%20counts%20of%20dereliction%20of%20duty%2C%20and%20not%20guilty%20for%20one%20count%20of%20obstruction%20of%20justice%2C%20though%20she%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20all%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Navy%20press%20office%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-chief-illegal-wifi-network-manchester-warship-named-stinky-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725441453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d81c6314a5cd1fcc8cf99b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-chief-illegal-wifi-network-manchester-warship-named-stinky-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grisel%20Marrero%20installed%20a%20Starlink%20network%20on%20the%20USS%20Manchester%20and%20named%20it%20%26quot%3BSTINKY%2C%26quot%3B%20sharing%20it%20with%20only%20the%20chief's%20mess%20while%20on%20deployment.%22%2C%2