0'Emergency'%20Stuck%20In%20Massive%20Row.%20What%20Are%20The%20Objections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20upcoming%20movie%20Emergency%20is%20caught%20in%20a%20controversy%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20objected%20to%20its%20release%20and%20accused%20the%20film's%20makers%20of%20misrepresenting%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20twisting%20historical%20facts.%20The%20actor%20and%20BJP%20MP%20has%20said%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20has%20put%20its%20clearance%20to%20the%20movie%20on%20hold%20after%20its%20members%20received%20death%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20'Emergency'%20About%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%2C%20starring%20Ms%20Ranaut%20in%20the%20lead%20role%2C%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20in%201975.%20Also%20starring%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20Shreyas%20Talpade%20and%20Milind%20Soman%2C%20it%20is%20a%20dramatic%20representation%20of%20the%2021-month%20period%20that%20is%20considered%20a%20dark%20phase%20for%20Indian%20democracy.%20It%20also%20touches%20upon%20Mrs%20Gandhi's%20assassination%20and%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20led%20by%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindranwale%20in%20the%201980s.%20The%20script%20has%20been%20written%20by%20Ms%20Ranaut%20and%20the%20film%20is%20co-produced%20by%20Zee%20Studios%20and%20the%20actor's%20Manikarnika%20Films.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20was%20earlier%20scheduled%20for%20a%20release%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it%20was%20postponed%20to%20June%20this%20year.%20Owing%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20it%20was%20postponed%20again%20and%20the%20release%20date%20was%20September%206.%20With%20the%20film%20now%20awaiting%20the%20Censor%20nod%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20when%20the%20movie%20will%20hit%20the%20screens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20The%20Objections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%2C%20an%20apex%20body%20managing%20Sikh%20religious%20institutions%2C%20has%20sent%20a%20legal%20notice%20to%20the%20film's%20producers.%20They%20have%20said%20that%20the%20movie%20misrepresents%20Sikhs%20and%20historical%20facts.%20A%20week%20after%20the%20film's%20trailer%20released%20last%20month%2C%20Akal%20Takht%20and%20SGPC%20demanded%20an%20immediate%20ban%20on%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20PTI%20report%2C%20SGPC%20secretary%20has%20said%20they%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20and%20the%20CBFC%2C%20seeking%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20film.%20The%20trailer%20had%20%26quot%3Banti-Sikh%26quot%3B%20scenes%20and%20this%20has%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurcharan%20Singh%20Grewal%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20SGPC%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20it%20is%20good%20that%20the%20Censor%20Board%20has%20halted%20the%20film's%20release.%20%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20pertains%20to%20not%20just%20Sikhs%2C%20but%20also%20concerns%20of%20harmony%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20government%20said%20some%20religious%20organisations%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20film.%20%26quot%3BReligious%20sentiments%20cannot%20be%20hurt.%20There%20is%20some%20sensitive%20content%20in%20the%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Centre%20was%20seriously%20looking%20at%20the%20concerns.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKangana%20Ranaut's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor-filmmaker%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bpressure%20on%20us%20not%20to%20depict%20the%20assassination%20of%20Mrs.%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Bhindrawale%2C%20and%20the%20Punjab%20riots%20in%20the%20film%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20raises%20the%20question%20-%20what%20can%20we%20actually%20show%20in%20the%20film%3F%20That%20the%20film%20blacks%20out%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20Netflix%20webseries%20IC%20814%2C%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said%20that%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20can%20show%20unimaginable%20amount%20of%20violence%20and%20nudity%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20without%20any%20consequence%20or%20censorship%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOne%20can%20even%20distort%20real%20life%20events%20to%20suit%20their%20politically%20motivated%20sinister%20motives%2C%20there%20is%20all%20the%20freedom%20for%20communists%20or%20leftists%20across%20the%20world%20for%20such%20anti%20national%20expressions%20but%20as%20a%20nationalist%20no%20OTT%20platform%20allows%20us%20to%20make%20films%20that%20revolves%20around%20the%20integrity%20and%20unity%20of%20Bharat%2C%20it%20seems%20censorship%20is%20only%20for%20some%20of%20us%20who%20don't%20want%20tukde%20of%20this%20nation%20and%20make%20films%20on%20historic%20facts.%20It's%20hugely%20demotivating%20and%20unjust%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMakers%20Move%20Court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%2C%20co-producer%20of%20the%20film%2C%20has%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20a%20direction%20to%20CBFC%20to%20issue%20the%20clearance%20certificate%20to%20'Emergency'.%20The%20court%20is%20hearing%20the%20matter.%20The%20petition%20has%20accused%20the%20Censor%20Board%20of%20%26quot%3Billegally%20and%20arbitrarily%26quot%3B%20withholding%20the%20film's%20certification.%20The%20Censor%20Board%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20certificate%20had%20been%20issued%2C%20but%20is%20now%20on%20hold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZee%20said%20CBFC%20is%20is%20taking%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20convenient%20half-measure%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20maker%20of%20the%20film%20is%20a%20sitting%20MP.%20They%20gave%20her%20a%20censor%20certificate%20and%20could%20have%20simply%20said%2C%20look%20we%20have%20given%20the%20censor%20certificate%20and%20now%20if%20there%20is%20unrest%2C%20the%20State%20can%20take%20care%20of%20the%20same.%20They%20cannot%20say%20that%20now%20that%20there%20is%20an%20unrest%2C%20we%20will%20rethink%20the%20certification%2C%26quot%3B%20Zee%20told%20the%20court.%20%26quot%3BCBFC%20is%20a%20censor%20body%20and%20not%20an%20authority%20to%20look%20after%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20State.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725438240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fuskevogo_kangana-emergency_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-stuck-in-massive-row-what-are-the-objections-6487046%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kangana%20Ranaut's%20upcoming%20movie%20Emergency%20is%20caught%20in%20a%20controversy%20after%20Sikh%20organisations%20objected%20to%20its%20release%20and%20accused%20the%20film's%20makers%20of%20misrepresenting%20the%20Sikh%20community%20and%20twisting%20historical%20facts%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telegram%20apologises%20for%20handling%20of%20deepfake%20porn%20material%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725438188000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F341b%2Flive%2F10b61250-6a8f-11ef-a788-4d91a3630157.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg45kz47dno%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20comes%20days%20after%20South%20Korean%20police%20said%20they%20had%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20Telegram.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg45kz47dno%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcvg45kz47dno.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%2