.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20are%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20that%20united%20the%20opposition%20ahead%20of%20the%20April-June%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20but%20the%20alliance%20has%20not%20been%20a%20key%20factor%20in%20state%20elections%20since%20it%20was%20formed%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20appears%20keen%20to%20change%20this%2C%20understanding%20the%20opposition%20stands%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20defeating%20the%20BJP%2C%20whether%20at%20the%20centre%20or%20state%2C%20if%20it%20stands%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-aap-alliance-in-haryana-negotiations-to-begin-soon-sources-6481958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAAP%2C%20Congress%20Alliance%20In%20Haryana%3F%20Seat%20Negotiations%20Begin%3A%20Sources%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%2C%20therefore%2C%20pressed%20the%20Congress'%20senior%20leaders%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20AAP%20for%20the%20Haryana%20election%20and%20guard%20against%20the%20division%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20talks%20last%20night%20said%20the%20AAP%20wants%20to%20contest%2010%20of%20the%20state's%2090%20seats.%20The%20Congress%2C%20though%2C%20was%20reluctant%20to%20concede%20more%20than%20seven%2C%20excluding%20one%20expected%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20ex%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20another%20INDIA%20bloc%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20talks%20are%20expected%20today%2C%20with%20the%20AAP's%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20the%20Congress'%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20both%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%2C%20handling%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EVinesh%20Phogat's%20Farmers%20Connect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20bringing%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20onboard%20strengthens%20its%20appeal%20among%20voters%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20state%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20ruled%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phogat's%20connect%20with%20Haryana%20farmers%20-%20lakhs%20of%20whom%20continue%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20issues%20like%20legal%20guarantees%20for%20MSP%20-%20will%20also%20have%20been%20a%20factor%20in%20the%20Congress'%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20Ms%20Phogat%20visited%20farmers%20camped%20out%20at%20a%20protest%20site%20in%20Shambhu%20on%20the%20Haryana-Delhi%20border%2C%20describing%20herself%20as%20%26quot%3Byour%20daughter%26quot%3B%20and%20saying%20she%20prays%20to%20God%20to%20deliver%20justice%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyour-daughter-stands-with-you-vinesh-phogat-at-farmers-protest-site-shambhu-border-6459537%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BYour%20Daughter%20Stands%20With%20You%26quot%3B%3A%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20At%20Farmers'%20Protest%20Site%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20agitation%20completes%20200%20days%20today.%20I%20pray%20to%20God%20that%20you%20get%20what%20you%20came%20for%20-%20justice.%20Your%20daughter%20stands%20with%20you.%20I%20also%20urge%20the%20government...%20we%20too%20are%20citizens%20of%20India%20and%20just%20because%20we%20raise%20our%20voices%20it%20is%20not%20political%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20(the%20government)%20should%20hear%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20though%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20her%20political%20debut%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20was%20circumspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhogat%2C%20Punia%2C%20Wrestlers%20Vs%20Brij%20Bhushan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phogat%20and%20Mr%20Punia%20made%20headlines%20last%20year%20after%20leading%20protests%20against%20former%20wrestling%20body%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20who%20faces%20charges%20of%20sexual%20assault%2