News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fv5erh83_gujarat-flood_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20and%20videos%20of%20crocodiles%20on%20roofs%2C%20on%20roads%2C%20and%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20University%20of%20Baroda%2C%20as%20well%20as%20roads%20caving%20in%20near%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity%20-%20a%20popular%20tourist%20attraction%20-%20and%20a%20viral%20video%20of%20a%20garba%20performance%20on%20Krishna%20Janmashtami%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20exemplify%20Gujarati%20resilience%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20turn%20adversity%20into%20celebration%20even%20during%20challenging%20times.%20Heavy%20rainfall%20has%20caused%20widespread%20disruption%20across%20Gujarat%2C%20leading%20to%20massive%20flooding%20and%20waterlogging%2C%20which%20has%20resulted%20in%20significant%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20property.%20As%20of%20August%2029%2C%20the%20official%20death%20toll%20from%20five%20days%20of%20torrential%20rain%20has%20reached%2047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20severely%20affected%20districts%20include%20Rajkot%2C%20Anand%2C%20Mahisagar%2C%20Kheda%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Morbi%2C%20Junagadh%2C%20and%20Bharuch.%20Several%20rivers%20and%20reservoirs%20in%20the%20state%20are%20overflowing.%20Water%20from%20the%20Ajwa%20and%20Pratappura%20reservoirs%20has%20been%20released%20into%20the%20Vishwamitri%20River%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20inundation%20of%20low-lying%20areas%20and%20severe%20waterlogging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%2C610%20km%20Of%20Roads%20Damaged%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStagnant%20water%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20diseases%20and%20illnesses.%20Even%20in%20an%20affluent%20city%20like%20Vadodara%2C%20crocodiles%20and%20other%20reptiles%20are%20being%20seen%20on%20main%20roads.%20From%20Kutch%20to%20Saurashtra%2C%20roads%20in%20towns%20and%20highways%20have%20caved%20in.%20Additionally%2C%20Gujarat%20is%20experiencing%20another%20spell%20of%20intense%20rainfall%20due%20to%20a%20deep%20depression%2C%20and%20the%20full%20impact%20will%20only%20be%20understood%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20requested%20the%20Army's%20assistance%20for%20urgent%20relief%20operations%20across%20several%20flood-affected%20districts.%20The%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20has%20already%20rescued%20hundreds%20of%20people%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20crisis.%20Due%20to%20damage%20caused%20by%20rain%20and%20floods%20to%20state%20and%20national%20highways%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupendra%20Patel%20has%20instructed%20the%20road%20construction%20department%20to%20expedite%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20(CMO)%2C%20repair%20work%20is%20underway%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20Local%20collectors%2C%20ministers%2Fsecretaries%20in-charges%2C%20and%20department%20coordinators%20are%20overseeing%20repair%20operations%20in%20all%20districts.%20Of%20a%20total%20of%201%2C16%2C000%20km%20of%20roads%20under%20the%20road%20and%20building%20department%2C%203%2C610%20km%20were%20damaged%20by%20the%20heavy%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disaster%20was%20partly%20a%20result%20of%20natural%20forces%2C%20but%20it%20also%20reflects%20a%20man-made%20crisis%2C%20considering%20Gujarat's%20history%20of%20urban%20flooding%2C%20particularly%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20due%20to%20illegal%20urbanisation%20and%20negligent%20city%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELack%20of%20Planning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vishwamitri%20River%2C%20which%20flows%20through%20Vadodara%2C%20is%20home%20to%20numerous%20crocodiles.%20Vadodara%20has%20experienced%20flooding%20due%20to%20river%20overflow%20in%202005%2C%202008%2C%202014%2C%20and%202019.%20Poor%20urban%20planning%20and%20oversight%20by%20the%20Vadodara%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(VMC)%20have%20led%20to%20residential%20colonies%20being%20built%20along%20the%20riverbanks%2C%20blocking%20and%20damaging%20the%20river%20ecosystem%20and%20contributing%20to%20flooding.%20Illegal%20dumping%20of%20construction%20and%20demolition%20waste%20on%20the%20riverbanks%20and%20ravines%20is%20rampant%2C%20yet%20the%20VMC%20has%20largely%20ignored%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEndemic%20corruption%20has%20led%20to%20encroachments%20on%20rivers%20and%20stormwater%20drains.%20The%20government%20has%20even%20allowed%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20mall%20right%20in%20the%20path%20of%20the%20Vishwamitri%20River%20in%20Vadodara.%20Similar%20examples%20exist%20in%20other%20major%20towns%20like%20Rajkot%20and%20Jamnagar%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Shaktisinh%20Gohil%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLarge%20sums%20are%20spent%20annually%20on%20paper%20for%20cleaning%20stormwater%20drains.%20If%20they%20were%20effectively%20cleaned%2C%20the%20state%20would%20not%20be%20facing%20the%20current%20man-made%20calamity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20devastation%20and%20public%20outcry%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20revive%20the%20long-stalled%20project%20to%20revitalise%20the%20Vishwamitri%20River.%20The%20Rs%201%2C200%20crore%20project%2C%20initially%20proposed%20in%202008%2C%20aims%20to%20expand%20the%20river's%20capacity%20and%20remove%20illegal%20encroachments%20along%20its%20banks.%20If%20executed%2C%20the%20Vishwamitri%20River%20Revival%20and%20Redevelopment%20project%20would%20involve%20widening%20the%20riverbed%2C%20constructing%20new%20embankments%2C%20and%20removing%20illegal%20structures%20obstructing%20the%20river's%20natural%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20ignored%20the%20suffering%20of%20its%20citizens.%20Those%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20homes%20and%20belongings%20are%20being%20compensated%20with%20Rs%205%2C000%20each%2C%20which%20is%20insufficient%20for%20families%20to%20sustain%20themselves%20without%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gohil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20concern%20about%20vector-borne%20diseases%2C%20such%20as%20dengue%2C%20zika%2C%20and%20chikungunya%2C%20due%20to%20water%20stagnation.%20Dengue-related%20deaths%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20August%2C%20and%20even%20medical%20students%20are%20falling%20ill%20due%20to%20water%20and%20vector-borne%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20source%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20the%20water%20recedes%2C%20a%20cleanliness%20drive%20will%20begin.%20The%20health%20department%20has%20been%20instructed%20to%20take%20preventive%20measures.%20Workers%20will%20check%20for%20stagnant%20water%20sites%2C%20and%20hospitals%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20prepare%20for%20potential%20emergencies%20or%20outbreaks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUrban%20Flooding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20must%20understand%20why%20urban%20flooding%20has%20become%20increasingly%20frequent%20given%20unpredictable%20rain%20patterns.%20The%20current%20rains%20are%20attributed%20to%20a%20deep%20depression%20over%20the%20coastal%20region%2C%20which%20experts%20consider%20unusual.%20A%20study%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20Institute%20of%20Disaster%20Management%20observed%20erratic%20precipitation%20patterns%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20with%20heavy%20rainfall%20days%20increasing%20and%20leading%20to%20flood-like%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Meteorological%20Department%20noted%20in%20January%202020%20that%2019%20districts%20in%20Gujarat%20have%20shown%20an%20increasing%20trend%20in%20overall%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh-intensity%20rainfall%20events%20are%20expected%20to%20become%20more%20frequent%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%20Authorities%2C%20urban%20experts%2C%20and%20environmentalists%20need%20to%20prepare%20for%20these%20eventualities.%20Our%20cities%20and%20towns%20require%20improved%20density%20rain%20gauge%20stations%20to%20record%20hourly%20rainfall%20intensity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20quality%20of%20civic%20infrastructure%2C%20such%20as%20roads%20and%20bridges%2C%20undermines%20our%20so-called%20development.%20This%20issue%20is%20not%20unique%20to%20Gujarat%3B%20other%20states%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Chennai%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20face%20similar%20challenges%20each%20monsoon%20season.%20Political%20will%2C%20educated%20and%20disciplined%20citizens%2C%20strict%20enforcement%20of%20civic%20laws%2C%20and%20flawless%20pre-monsoon%20preparedness%20are%20crucial%20to%20preventing%20repeated%20disasters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725434700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjbi161p8_gujarat-flood_625x300_04_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcrocodiles-road-cave-ins-gujarat-infra-is-facing-a-monsoon-test-6487378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20in%20an%20affluent%20city%20like%20Vadodara%2C%20crocodiles%20and%20other%20reptiles%20are%20being%20seen%20on%20main%20roads.%20From%20Kutch%20to%20Saurashtra%2C%20several%20roads%20in%20towns%20and%20highways%20have%20caved%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcrocodiles-road-cave-ins-gujarat-infra-is-facing-a-monsoon-test-6487378%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20reveals%20Android%20features%20including%20Music%20Search%20in%20Circle%20to%20Search%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725434611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F04%