20history%2C%20is%20known%20for%20his%20extravagant%20lifestyle.%20One%20of%20his%20most%20notable%20possessions%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20private%20car%20collection.%20Valued%20at%20%245%20billion%2C%20his%20collection%20features%20over%207%2C000%20luxury%20cars%2C%20reported%20Fox%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collection%20was%20put%20together%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Hassanal's%20brother%2C%20Jefri%20Bolkiah%20(also%20known%20as%20Prince%20Jefri)%2C%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family.%20Since%20it's%20impossible%20to%20talk%20about%20every%20car%20he%20owns%2C%20we'll%20focus%20on%20a%20select%20few%20luxury%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bentleys%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESultan's%20car%20collection%20includes%20approximately%20%2480%20million%20worth%20of%20classic%20Bentleys%20from%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%2C%20mostly%20Azure%20and%20Continental%20models.%20The%20Bentley%20Dominator%20SUV%20is%20among%20the%20most%20unique%20among%20the%20selection.%20Other%20Bentley%20cars%20in%20the%20collection%20include%20the%20Continental%20R%20Superfast%2C%20the%20Buccaneer%20GT%20coupe%2C%20and%20the%20Java%2C%20which%20has%20a%20twin-turbo%20V8%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ferraris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20shortage%20of%20Italian%20exotica%20in%20the%20largest%20vehicle%20collection%20in%20the%20world.%20He%20owns%20a%20rare%20Ferrari%20F50%2C%20two%20250%20GTOs%2C%20an%20F40%2C%20several%20Ferrari%20456s%2C%20a%20Ferrari%20FX%20and%20a%20Testarossa%20F90%20Speciale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Porsches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sultan's%20collection%20also%20includes%2055%20Porsche%20928s%2C%2032%20of%20which%20are%20S4%20variants.%20This%20demonstrates%20how%20Porsche%20has%20successfully%20branched%20out%20from%20its%20classic%20911%20model.%20The%20monarch%20also%20got%20a%20Porsche%20959s%2C%20a%20Daur%20962%20Le%20Mans%20and%20a%20Carrera%20GT%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Rolls-Royces%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20Sultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%20broke%20the%20record%20for%20having%20the%20world's%20largest%20private%20Rolls-Royce%20collection.%20Though%20the%20precise%20number%20is%20unknown%2C%20estimations%20indicate%20that%20there%20are%20more%20than%20600%20distinct%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aston%20Martins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sultan%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20ordering%20custom%20Aston%20Martin%20vehicles.%20The%20unique%20AM3%2C%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20grand%20tourer%20inspired%20by%20the%20Vantage%20and%20created%20in%20association%20with%20Pininfarina%2C%20is%20one%20noteworthy%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20Sultan's%20opulent%20collection%20features%20several%20McLaren%2C%20Bugatti%2C%20BMW%2C%20Mercedes-Benz%2C%20Brabus%2C%20Jaguar%20and%20a%20Koenigsegg%20CCXR.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725431400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmhl4nkig_sultan-hassanal-bolkiah_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F7-000-and-counting-a-look-at-sultan-of-bruneis-5-billion-car-collection-6487015%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sultan%20Of%20Brunei's%20car%20collection%20boasts%20more%20than%207%2C000%20vehicles%20and%20is%20worth%20an%20estimated%20%245%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Huang%20replies%20to%20being%20called%20%E2%80%98demanding%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98not%20easy%20to%20work%20for'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725431225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113053203%2Cimgsize-2154300.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwa