%20Show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudies%20have%20found%20that%20nose%20breathing%20can%20indeed%20benefit%20health.%20A%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.physiology.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1152%2Fajpregu.00148.2023%3Futm_source%3DAJPRegu%26utm_medium%3DPressRelease%26utm_campaign%3D1.17.2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%20the%20American%20Journal%20of%20Physiology%20found%20that%20nose%20breathing%20can%20lower%20blood%20pressure%20and%20reduce%20risk%20factors%20for%20heart%20disease.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F7939149%2F%23full-view-affiliation-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Goteborg%20found%20that%20nasal%20breathing%20can%20decrease%20snoring%20and%20alleviate%20sleep%20apnea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20TikTok%2C%20users%20have%20turned%20to%20mouth%20tapes%20to%20seal%20their%20mouths%20shut%20to%20promote%20nose%20breathing.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%2011%2C200%20posts%20under%20the%20hashtag%20%23mouthtape.%20Users%20who%20have%20tried%20mouth%20taping%20said%20it%20leads%20to%20deeper%20sleep%2C%20better%20oral%20hygiene%2C%20and%20reduced%20snoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20no%20conclusive%20research%20proves%20these%20purported%20benefits%20of%20mouth%20taping%2C%20and%20experts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmouth-taping-for-sleep-oral-health-doctors-warn-of-risks-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecautioned%20against%20the%20trend%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213e8be0d-23f2-45f4-8886-9330880027d2%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20other%20ways%20to%20get%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20of%20getting%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep%20have%20been%20emphasized%20time%20and%20again.%20Good%20quality%20sleep%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-longevity-supplements-vs-exercise-and-diet-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-longevity-supplements-vs-exercise-and-diet-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20heart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20better%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgood-sleep-routine-avoid-burnout-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20well-being%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20getting%20there%20takes%20effort.%20Dr.%20Mathias%20Basner%2C%20a%20sleep%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-getting-better-sleep-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20maintaining%20an%20established%20mundane%20nighttime%20routine%20can%20help%20one%20wind%20down%20for%20bed.%20The%20routine%20can%20include%20brushing%20one's%20teeth%20or%20putting%20away%20the%20dishes%2C%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20too%20stimulating%2C%20Basner%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20for%20better%20sleep%20is%20to%20journal%20before%20bed.%20Doing%20so%20can%20help%20to%20release%20anxious%20thoughts%2C%20Dr.%20Meena%20Khan%2C%20a%20neurologist%20and%20sleep%20expert%20at%20Ohio%20State%20University%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20sit%20down%20and%20write%20down%20a%20list%20of%20things%20that%20are%20bothering%20you%2C%20a%20list%20of%20things%20you%20have%20to%20do%2C%20so%20you're%20going%20through%20it%20before%20bed%20rather%20than%20processing%20it%20in%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20breathing%20exercises%20before%20bed%20can%20help%20you%20sleep%20better.%20In%202020%2C%20BI%20reported%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-healt